{"name":"Diehard","type":"feat","img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/skills.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<div>\n\t\t\t\t<p><i>Prerequisite: Tactician Field of Study</i></p>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You gain 1 maximum hit point for every level you have in the scholar class. Whenever you gain a new level in the scholar class your maximum hit points increase by 1. Additionally, you add your proficiency bonus to death saving throws.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>\n\t\t\t</div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"BH:SC","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":0,"long":0,"units":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Tactician Field of Study","recharge":{"value":0,"charged":true}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"UMdjDmtPw3ghSmh7":3},"flags":{"srd5e":{"page":"optionalfeatures.html","source":"BH:SC","hash":"diehard_bh%3asc","propDroppable":"optionalfeature"}},"_id":"0dOd9ANAXLA7MHeo"}
{"name":"Verbum Dei","type":"feat","img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/skills.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<div>\n\t\t\t\t<p><i>Prerequisite: Theologian Field of Study</i></p>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>As an action, you utter holy words no mortal was meant to say. When you do, each creature within 30 feet of you who can hear you (including yourself) must succeed a Wisdom saving throw or take [[/r 3d6]] radiant damage. This damage increases by 2d6 at 5th level ([[/r 5d6]]), 11th level ([[/r 7d6]]), and 17th level ([[/r 9d6]]). The DC for this saving throw equals 8 + your proficiency bonus + your Intelligence modifier. The damage from this erudite application is doubled against aberrations, celestials, elementals, fey, fiends, and undead creatures.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p>Once you use this erudite application, you must finish a short or long rest before you can use it again.</p></div>\n\t\t\t</div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"BH:SC","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":0,"long":0,"units":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Theologian Field of Study","recharge":{"value":0,"charged":true}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"UMdjDmtPw3ghSmh7":3},"flags":{"srd5e":{"page":"optionalfeatures.html","source":"BH:SC","hash":"verbum%20dei_bh%3asc","propDroppable":"optionalfeature"}},"_id":"1VKYaUl7YQVo2E3W"}
{"name":"Seal Agreement","type":"feat","img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/skills.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<div>\n\t\t\t\t<p><i>Prerequisite: Diplomat Field of Study</i></p>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You can cast the @spell[oath-sealing covenant|BH:SC] spell at will without expending a spell slot and the materials required. You use Intelligence as your spellcasting ability for this spell.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>\n\t\t\t</div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"BH:SC","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":0,"long":0,"units":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Diplomat Field of Study","recharge":{"value":0,"charged":true}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"UMdjDmtPw3ghSmh7":3},"flags":{"srd5e":{"page":"optionalfeatures.html","source":"BH:SC","hash":"seal%20agreement_bh%3asc","propDroppable":"optionalfeature"}},"_id":"1x9ZSLsJnAkw9Nw7"}
{"name":"Clean Plate Practice","type":"feat","img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/skills.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<div>\n\t\t\t\t<p><i>Prerequisite: Culinarian Field of Study</i></p>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You can spend 1 minute assessing a food or drink to determine whether it is poisonous or diseased. If it is, you know the poison or disease. You can spend 10 minutes to render all food and drink within 5 feet of you free of poison and disease.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>\n\t\t\t</div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"BH:SC","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":0,"long":0,"units":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Culinarian Field of Study","recharge":{"value":0,"charged":true}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"UMdjDmtPw3ghSmh7":3},"flags":{"srd5e":{"page":"optionalfeatures.html","source":"BH:SC","hash":"clean%20plate%20practice_bh%3asc","propDroppable":"optionalfeature"}},"_id":"1yUofHmwHBh14inT"}
{"name":"Critical Analysis","type":"feat","img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/skills.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>When you use your Analyze Enemy feature on a creature, any attack roll you make against that creature for the next minute is a critical hit on a roll of 19 or 20 on the d20. At 11th level, your attack rolls against such a creature are a critical hit on a roll of 18, 19, or 20.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>\n\t\t\t</div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"BH:SC","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":0,"long":0,"units":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":0,"charged":true}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"UMdjDmtPw3ghSmh7":3},"flags":{"srd5e":{"page":"optionalfeatures.html","source":"BH:SC","hash":"critical%20analysis_bh%3asc","propDroppable":"optionalfeature"}},"_id":"3dlUlW37FMLe5LnN"}
{"name":"Cunning Linguist","type":"feat","img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/skills.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<div>\n\t\t\t\t<p><i>Prerequisite: Diplomat Field of Study</i></p>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>When you have the opportunity to study written or spoken examples of a language for 8 hours, you can choose to learn to that language. You can speak, read, and write that language until you use this erudite application again.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>\n\t\t\t</div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"BH:SC","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":0,"long":0,"units":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Diplomat Field of Study","recharge":{"value":0,"charged":true}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"UMdjDmtPw3ghSmh7":3},"flags":{"srd5e":{"page":"optionalfeatures.html","source":"BH:SC","hash":"cunning%20linguist_bh%3asc","propDroppable":"optionalfeature"}},"_id":"4O4UvEwCvGqtGwSO"}
{"name":"Academic Expertise","type":"feat","img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/skills.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>Choose two of the following skills you are proficient in: <span class=\"help help--hover\" data-plut-hover=\"true\" data-plut-hover-preload=\"true\" data-plut-hover-preload-id=\"10\">Arcana</span>, <span class=\"help help--hover\" data-plut-hover=\"true\" data-plut-hover-preload=\"true\" data-plut-hover-preload-id=\"11\">History</span>, <span class=\"help help--hover\" data-plut-hover=\"true\" data-plut-hover-preload=\"true\" data-plut-hover-preload-id=\"12\">Investigation</span>, <span class=\"help help--hover\" data-plut-hover=\"true\" data-plut-hover-preload=\"true\" data-plut-hover-preload-id=\"13\">Medicine</span>, <span class=\"help help--hover\" data-plut-hover=\"true\" data-plut-hover-preload=\"true\" data-plut-hover-preload-id=\"14\">Nature</span>, or <span class=\"help help--hover\" data-plut-hover=\"true\" data-plut-hover-preload=\"true\" data-plut-hover-preload-id=\"15\">Religion</span>. Your proficiency bonus is doubled for any ability check you make that uses either of the chosen proficiencies.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>\n\t\t\t</div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"BH:SC","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":0,"long":0,"units":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":0,"charged":true}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"UMdjDmtPw3ghSmh7":3},"flags":{"srd5e":{"page":"optionalfeatures.html","source":"BH:SC","hash":"academic%20expertise_bh%